headline: Take-Two Scores Price-Target Hikes On 'NBA 2K26,' 'Grand Theft Auto 6' Games
summary: TTWO stock is trading in record-high territory on investor enthusiasm for Take-Two Interactive Software’s current and upcoming video games.
